Dialogue: 4,0:02:52.46,0:02:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V-Vyzeráš úplne rovnako ako Cordelia.
Dialogue: 4,0:02:57.68,0:03:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bola som vtedy ešte len dieťa, ale dobre si ju pamätám!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:01.37,0:03:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Harminia!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:02.79,0:03:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hriešna Cordelia...
Dialogue: 4,0:03:05.29,0:03:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Z tohoto sídla... z tejto dediny jej kliatba nikdy neodíde!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Harminia!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ospravedlňte ma.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo s tou ženskou je?
Dialogue: 4,0:03:24.04,0:03:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onen incident sa stal v študovni starostu Theodora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.68,Sign-EpNumber,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,186)\fs32\fscy100\c&HFEFEFE&}Epizóda 7
