Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.68,Sign-EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,510)\blur0.3\fs46\fscx86\c&HFEFEFE&}Je Vyslovené Proroctvo
Dialogue: 4,0:03:27.68,0:03:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tej dobe tam bola služobná...
Dialogue: 4,0:03:31.66,0:03:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno, Cordelia, ktorá vtedy mala len 15 rokov.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:35.65,0:03:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chodievala tam vymieňať vodu vo vázach.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj v tú noc, prišla tam presne o 12:00.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako viete, že to bolo {\i1}presne{\i0\fscx150} {\r}vtedy?
Dialogue: 4,0:03:45.59,0:03:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja a niekoľko ďalších ľudí videlo\NCordeliu použiť kľúč a otvoriť dvere.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:51.47,0:03:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Práve vtedy som pozeral na hodinky.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:55.61,0:04:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale, z nejakého dôvodu všetci ostatní hovorili o inom čase.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:01.86,0:04:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hneď po vstupe do študovne\N Cordelia zakričala a vybehla von.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rýchlo som pribehol do izby.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:08.69,0:04:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starosta Theodore bol bodnutý nožom\N a dýchal naposledy.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:13.73,0:04:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neviem prečo, ale na podlahe bolo veľa rozosiatých zlatých mincí.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zlaté mince?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:20.36,0:04:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starosta Theodore ich zbieral,\N aby sa v tejto dedine nepoužívali.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:28.10,0:04:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Od tej noci, Cordelia dlho ležala so silnou horúčkou v posteli.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:32.35,0:04:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potom som počkal, kým jej horúčka ustúpi, a ako nasledujúci starosta som ju vyhnal.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyhnal?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:45.76,0:04:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dostala jednu zlatú mincu a jeden kufor.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:50.42,0:04:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zdvihli sme jej most.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:53.14,0:04:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bolo to naivné dievča, \Nktoré nikdy nepoložilo nohu na vonkajší svet.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neboli sme si istí, či prežije, ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hrozné.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S hriešnikom sa musí vysporiadať.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inak by na dedinu padlo nešťastie.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:09.48,0:05:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale, dcéra Cordelie je práve teraz tu.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, Victorique!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prechádzka?! Veď sme sem len prišli!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique, no tak!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ste na prechádzke?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno...
Dialogue: 4,0:05:25.47,0:05:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som asistent starostu Sergiusa, Ambrose.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um.. Um...
Dialogue: 4,0:05:32.41,0:05:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nebojte sa, len som zvedavý, \Nprečo máte inú farbu kože a vlasov.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:35.73,0:05:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Viem, že všetci vo vonkajšom svete nemajú blond vlasy, ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique, pomôž mi!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rada by som,\N keby si ma doviedol na určité miesto.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno. Nebojte sa a hovorte.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mohol by som sa ho na oplátku \Nešte chvíľu dotýkať?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rob ako chceš.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:53.78,0:05:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vi—
Dialogue: 4,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže, kam?
Dialogue: 4,0:05:57.08,0:06:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do domu, kde bývala Cordelia.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu to je.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja teraz odídem.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Odchádzate?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:10.93,0:06:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevadilo mu nás niekam doviesť, \Nkým sa nedozvedel, že to bolo tu.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:37.38,0:06:38.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pomôž mi s tým.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:38.88,0:06:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Á-Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to je?!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale nič tam nie je—
Dialogue: 4,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Táto fotka...
Dialogue: 4,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cordelia?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ja, keď som bola dieťa.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:04.13,0:07:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale Cordelia bola vyhnaná, keď mala len pätnásť, nie?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niekto sem prišiel.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zobral to, čo tu bolo,
Dialogue: 4,0:07:13.88,0:07:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a vymenil to za fotku dospelej Cordelie.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kam tento chaos smeruje?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:26.89,0:07:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Theodore...
Dialogue: 4,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hrob predchádzajúceho starostu, hm?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To nemôžeš, Victorique!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeš vykopávať hroby...
