Dialogue: 4,0:07:42.34,0:07:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Som nevinná. C..."
Dialogue: 4,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cordelia?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten, kto to napísal je Cordelia!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:54.47,0:07:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moja matka bola predsa len z tejto dediny vyhnaná za zločin, ktorý nevykonala!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tom prípade...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:05.39,0:08:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kde je skutočný vinník?!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:08.26,0:08:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:09.75,0:08:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kujō?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Utekaj!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kujō?!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To nie je smiech.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...rovnaká farba ako Victoriquine oči...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zachránili sme sa.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vlci...?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ako išiel hovor?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale... to ste len vy.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa stalo?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-Mildred-san...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hovor? Je na tomto mieste elektrina?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:03.42,0:09:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno! Starosta povedal, že sú sebestační.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:07.19,0:09:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno. Zdalo sa mi, že je tu niečo divné, tak som sa opýtala tej divnej služobnej.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vraj že majú sponzora.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sponzora?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:15.79,0:09:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno. Akože sa to volal?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brian...
Dialogue: 4,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Brian Roscoe.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brian... Roscoe...
Dialogue: 4,0:09:27.00,0:09:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vraj že je to potomok niekoho, \Nkto dedinu opustil a odišiel žiť von.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:30.99,0:09:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pred desiatimi rokmi \Ntejto dedine vraj dal peniaze.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pred desiatimi rokmi...
Dialogue: 4,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Karty už ma nudia.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, pozrime sa do kostola.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale pred chvíľou tam boli vlci...
Dialogue: 4,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vlci?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:47.33,0:09:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevadí! Veď ich odoženie ten podivný starec, nie?
Dialogue: 4,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak, poďme!
Dialogue: 4,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zase sa to zaplietlo.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Točí sa mi hlava z toho, koľko tu je ozdôbok a mašličiek.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, Victorique...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:03.08,0:10:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brian Roscoe, ktorý sem prišiel pred desiatimi rokmi...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:07.28,0:10:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Z akého dôvodu sem prišiel?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dôvod?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, chcel do dediny zaviesť elektrinu, nie?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:15.35,0:10:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Veď vieš, že pred desiatimi rokmi sa začala Svetová vojna.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:20.89,0:10:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemyslíš si, že je v takom čase divné do \Nnejakej dediny v horách zavádzať elektrinu?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okrem toho...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:28.24,0:10:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pred desiatimi rokmi je aj čas, kedy bola urobená táto fotografia.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Á-Áno?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doniesla som vám vodu na kúpeľ.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pred použitím ju ochlaďte studenou vodou.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžem sa tu aj vykúpať?!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:45.55,0:10:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique, ak sa niečo stane, tak mi hneď povedz, hej?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som hneď tu.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique?!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:01.03,0:11:04.39,Dialogue-Top,,0,0,0,,Miiiiiiiilujem kúpele!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Och, len si spieva...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.94,Dialogue-Top,,0,0,0,,Sú tak krásne a teplé!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to, že sa znova vrátila do normálu.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiež si chcem trochu vydýchnuť.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo...?!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Č-Čo sa stalo?!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, Victorique! Si v poriadku?!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neodpovedá...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je, Kujō?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si hlučný.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:43.92,0:11:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niekto ma chce vystrašiť a odohnať od dediny.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vráťme sa!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:49.51,0:11:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Z tejto dediny mám zlý pocit.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:51.68,0:11:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to tu nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja sa nevrátim.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:56.74,0:11:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Veď ma ochrániš, však?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Samozrejme!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak to sa nemusím báť.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:29.55,0:12:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Úžasné...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je červená repa.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tieto vozy patria Armáde zimy.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Armáda zimy?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:37.36,0:12:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Muži z dediny hrajú boj, kde proti sebe pôjdu Armáda zimy a Armáda leta.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:41.36,0:12:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Armáda leta porazí generála Armády zimy, Zimného Muža, a zapáli tieto vozy.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:49.19,0:12:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak chcete túto dedinu ohovárať, odíďte!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hlúposti!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:53.07,0:12:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vážne hnusná dedina, že jej ľudia veria takýmto hlúpostiam!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Však?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:58.30,0:13:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo ak nás teraz vyženú?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Prepáčte!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všade, kde chodí hľadá bitky!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vráťme sa do izieb, hej?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:14.83,0:13:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tí hlupáci. Robili rozruch aj včera večer v kostole.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pred očami spústy dedinčanov...
Dialogue: 4,0:13:20.99,0:13:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hodilli starý ornamentálny džbán do svätenej vody.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo to urobili?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechápem logiku opilcov.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:32.92,0:13:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ešte sa aj smiali, "Prečo si nechávajú takú starú blbosť?".
Dialogue: 4,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj keď sa im páčilo, že je to tu retro...
Dialogue: 4,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na, doniesol som ti nejaké sladkosti.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pripravte sa!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Auvajs!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto to je?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alan-san.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj po tom, čo všeto povedal, ho tento festival zaujíma.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:09.42,0:14:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, som zvedavý, čo to znamená.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ooh! To je Ambrose-san?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá úžasne!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zimný Muž, zhor a strať sa!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to je?!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten strašiak...!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:53.46,0:14:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pozor, pozor!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vodu!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alan-san!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:35.69,0:15:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alan...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bola to nehoda.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:38.59,0:15:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aby vyrušil festival a naštval nás, tak sa pravdepodobne vymenil so strašiakom.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:43.37,0:15:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hlúpy hosť.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je hlúposť!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starosta Sergius, to nie je možné.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:49.29,0:15:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tento človek sa tu ešte prechádzal, keď dievčatá hádzali lieskovce.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:54.30,0:15:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A na námestí bolo veľa ľudí, takže nie je možné, aby sa vymenil so strašiakom...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Utáranosť je hriech hlupákov.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:04.24,0:16:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ospravedlňujem sa.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:08.04,0:16:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeme si dovoliť zastaviť festival.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:11.08,0:16:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V kostole budeme mať ceremóniu, tak ma ospravedlňte.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkaj! Hej!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:23.02,0:16:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako môžu s festivalom pokračovať aj po tom, čo niekto zomrel?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:26.72,0:16:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ľudia z tejto dediny sú predsa len divní.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:29.51,0:16:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Však, Victorique?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Victorique?
Dialogue: 4,0:16:47.81,0:16:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Veď ma ochrániš, však?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:09.41,0:17:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuya-san, prišiel si sa opýtať na svoju budúcnosť?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Budúcnosť?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:14.81,0:17:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Armáda leta vyhrala, a veľká úroda bola zaručená.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže kostol bude až do večera voľný.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tento kostol je bočná brána do druhého sveta.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:23.82,0:17:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to miesto, ktorým prechádzajú naši predkovia, keď nám ukazujú dobrú úrodu.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale ešte pred tým, čo sa do našeho sveta dostanú,
Dialogue: 4,0:17:30.70,0:17:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hovoria cez ústa starostu, a odpovedajú na otázky detí.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:35.53,0:17:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuya-san, prišiel si sem, takže...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Um, ja len hľadám Victorique...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:43.23,0:17:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Počkaj, Ambrose-san!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto si?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:56.50,0:17:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, ja hľadám Victorique...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tom prípade sa nemáš o čo báť.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:01.48,0:18:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To dievča je od teba iné.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže, čo sa chceš opýtať?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:10.00,0:18:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vlastne, mám jednu kamarátku...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:14.33,0:18:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžem odteraz s Victorique...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...už navždy byť spolu?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spolu nezomriete.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:29.59,0:18:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niekoľko rokov odteraz...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:31.84,0:18:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...bude fúkať vietor tak silný, že otrasie samotným svetom.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vaše telá sú ľahké...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:40.64,0:18:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten silný vietor vás rozdelí.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:50.22,0:18:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...vaše srdcia budú vždy spolu.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naše srdcia...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To znamená...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďalší!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Budeme oddelení...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bola si tu aj ty?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:26.98,0:19:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Č-Čo si sa opýtala?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Opýtala som sa, či vyrastiem.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:34.80,0:19:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyrastieš? Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Výška.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Výška?!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to s tebou je?!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:43.31,0:19:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ani netušíš, čo som sa opýtal ja...
Dialogue: 4,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ach jo, už je to jedno!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:47.17,0:19:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo si taký naštvaný?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:48.85,0:19:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem uveriť, že si mi nič nepovedala.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kde si doteraz bola?!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V študovni.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maman...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hriešna Cordelia!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:13.58,0:20:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starosta Theodore bol zavraždený takto, mal dýkou prerazený chrbát.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetko, aj ornamenty na tej dýke sa mi vrylo do pamäti.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starosta Theodore bol dospelý.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cordelia bola pätnásťročné dievča.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mali aj rôznu výšku.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je pravda.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:30.07,0:20:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pre dieťa je nemožné zabodnúť dýku do ramena dospelého, keď tam ani nedosiahne.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hriešna Cordelia...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tá pošpinená duša...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale čo ak... čo ak...
Dialogue: 4,0:20:41.64,0:20:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je vinník niekto iný.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:44.13,0:20:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslíš si to aj ty?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:13.61,0:21:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prehovoril ku mne prameň múdrosti.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:16.23,0:21:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetky časti boli rekonštruované!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rekonštruované?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže si prišla na to, kto je vinník?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:24.76,0:21:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak to aj viem, tak nie je spôsob, ako to dokázať.
Dialogue: 4,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ukázali sa vlci?
Dialogue: 4,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak aj niekto zomrie...
Dialogue: 4,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak aj prídu vlci...
Dialogue: 4,0:21:43.92,0:21:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nedovolím, aby bol festival zastavený!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:47.52,0:21:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nasledujme ich!
Dialogue: 4,0:21:49.08,0:21:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victorique!
Dialogue: 4,0:22:01.74,0:22:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vlky už nepočujeme, hm?
Dialogue: 4,0:22:05.35,0:22:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tam!
Dialogue: 4,0:22:07.80,0:22:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie! Nerobte to!
